âœ¨ Features
AI Chat: Conversation with ChatGPT (/gpt)

Quiz Game: Interactive quizzes on various topics (/quiz)

Random Facts: Interesting fact generator (/random)

Character Chat: Talk with historical/popular figures (/talk)

Translation: Multi-language text translation (/translate)

Voice Interaction: Voice message processing (/voice)

ğŸ›  Installation
Clone the repository:

bash
git clone https://github.com/MrJonson75/GPT_Telegramm_bot.git
cd mybot
Install dependencies:

bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Install FFmpeg (for voice processing):

bash
# On Ubuntu/Debian
sudo apt install ffmpeg

# On MacOS
brew install ffmpeg
âš™ Configuration
Create .env file:

bash
cp .env.example .env
Edit .env with your credentials:

ini
TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token
GPT_TOKEN=your_openai_api_key
PROXY=your_proxy_server_if_needed  # Optional
ğŸš€ Usage
Start the bot:

bash
python app.py
Available Commands:
Command	Description
/start	Show main menu
/gpt	Chat with AI
/quiz	Start quiz game
/random	Get random fact
/talk	Talk with characters
/translate	Translate text
/voice	Voice interaction
